sequenceDiagram
    participant Admin as Central Admin/Schedule
    participant Orchard as Integration Test (Central)
    participant Consumer as Consumer Repo (CI)

    Admin->>Orchard: Trigger integration-test.yml
    
    par For Each Repo (Matrix)
        Orchard->>Consumer: API Trigger (workflow_dispatch)
        
        loop Polling Status
            Orchard->>Consumer: Check Run Status
            Consumer-->>Orchard: "in_progress"
        end
        
        Consumer-->>Orchard: "completed" (success/fail)
    end
    
    Orchard->>Orchard: Aggregate Results
    Orchard->>Admin: Report Summary (PR Comment / Log)
